MediaWiki Purpose Centric Search Extension

==Prerequisites==
* Downloaded the extension from SVN
* MediaWiki 1.19+
* Install following extensions:
  1. Flagged Revs
	2. W4GratingBar
	3. Infobox Template
* Download Wordnet 3.0

==Setup==
* Add the following lines to 'LocalSettings.php':
	require_once( "$IP/extensions/PurposeCentricSearch/PurposeCentricSearch.php" );
	$wgWordnetPath = "<Path of Wordnet bin>";
* Run 'maintenance/update.php' to add the SQL column to page table

